%% Diagram: Multi Layer Caching Eliminates 99 9 Of Redundant Processing Only The First Reque
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Cache Layers"
        CDN["CDN Edge\n95% hit rate"]
        Redis["Redis\n80% of misses"]
        DB["DB Index\n90% of remainder"]
        Process["Transform\n< 5% of requests"]
    end

    Request --> CDN
    CDN -->|5% miss| Redis
    Redis -->|20% miss| DB
    DB -->|10% miss| Process
    Process -->|store| DB
